Package: scLASER
Title: Single-Cell Longitudinal Analysis, Simulation, and Visualization
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(
      person(given = "Juan", family = "Vargas", role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "your_email@cuanschutz.edu"),
      person(given = "Fan",  family = "Zhang",  role = "aut",
             email = "fanzhanglab@gmail.com")
    )
Description: Tools for modeling, simulating, and visualizing single-cell longitudinal datasets,
    including mixed-effects modeling with time as continuous/categorical/quadratic and automated model selection.
